name: Darkwing Duck 2
overview: He is the terror that flaps in the night… and he's returned! Catch Darkwing Duck, Launchpad McQuack, Gosalyn, and more in this fan made sequel. The Terror that Flaps in the Night clashes with a villain who may be unstoppable, and faces off with his arch nemesis Megavolt and Negaduck as they wreak havoc on the city.
